      <item>
        <title>Blog: Time to change your apps</title>
        <description>&lt;!--more--&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;샘플 코드 : https://github.com/Pluu/VersionCodeUpdaterSample&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;방법-1-defaultconfig-속성-수정&quot;&gt;방법 1) defaultConfig 속성 수정&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-kotlin highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// app/build.gradle.kts&lt;/span&gt;
